      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm studying for my theory exam and i'm a bit stuck. why do certain intervals like a minor second sound so \"unpleasant\" or \"unstable\" compared to something like a perfect fifth? like, is there a specific physical reason behind the dissonance?",
      "source": "evaluator"
