      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, what? i don't get the goblin thing lol. can you just stick to the acoustics part? i'm specifically looking for the technical explanation involving frequency ratios and the actual interference patterns (like beating) that happen in the ear. can you explain how that works without the metaphors?",
      "source": "evaluator"
